
Spanish rice

Base ingredients

Drizzle olive oil for frying.
1/2 onion chopped.
1 tsp salt.
1 tsp Pig powder

Fry 'till onions are getting clear then add..

3 tbl tomato pasta sauce (From a Jar, any brand you like)
1 bowl garlic.

Stir this around for a minute or so then..

Add 2 cups rice.

Siri this around 'till everything is mixed together.
By now thing should be really hot.

Dump in 2 schooners of water. (30 oz)

Bring to boil.

Burner down to low, cover 15 min.
Shut off, 15 min still covered.
Open and fluf.